<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>绮梦娃衣 - 定制你的微缩浪漫</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #d4a373; /* 奶茶金 */
            --bg-color: #fefae0;      /* 奶油色背景 */
            --text-color: #606c38;    /* 深橄榄绿文字 */
            --accent-color: #bc6c25;  /* 焦糖色 */
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-color);
            margin: 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 100px 20px;
            /* 这里预设了一个背景图，你可以之后换成自己的娃片 */
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.3)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558017487-06bf9f82613a?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1000') center/cover;
            color: white;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 8px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 50px 20px;
        }

        h2 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin: 50px 0 30px;
            position: relative;
        }

        h2::after {
            content: '';
            display: block;
            width: 50px;
            height: 3px;
            background: var(--primary-color);
            margin: 10px auto;
        }

        /* 橱窗网格 */
        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 1px solid rgba(212, 163, 115, 0.2);
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
        }

        .card img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 400px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .card-info {
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .card-info h3 { margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: var(--accent-color); }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background-color: var(--accent-color);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }

        .btn:hover { background-color: var(--primary-color); }

        /* 定制流程 */
        .process {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .process-item { flex: 1; min-width: 200px; padding: 20px; }
        .process-item i { font-size: 2rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 10px; }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            background: #e9edc6;
            margin-top: 80px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        /* 手机适配 */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            header h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; }
            .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>绮梦娃衣</h1>
        <p>—— 缝补时光，留住指尖的童话 ——</p>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <h2>✨ 现货/预约橱窗</h2>
        <div class="grid">
            <div class="card">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1594913223275-c288930438f4?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=500" alt="复古宫廷裙">
                <div class="card-info">
                    <h3>【维多利亚的午后】</h3>
                    <p>精致蕾丝与丝绒的碰撞<br>适用：OB11 / GSC</p>
                    <a href="#" class="btn">立即私信</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1583946028527-39614307d10c?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=500" alt="学院风套装">
                <div class="card-info">
                    <h3>【冬日格纹祭】</h3>
                    <p>暖融融的羊毛呢材质<br>适用：20cm 棉花娃</p>
                    <a href="#" class="btn">查看库存</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555529733-0e670560f7e1?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=500" alt="云朵睡裙">
                <div class="card-info">
                    <h3>【云端漫步】</h3>
                    <p>轻盈如蝉翼的真丝裙<br>适用：BJD 6分/4分</p>
                    <a href="#" class="btn">款式定制</a>
               
